quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  72,14,"E won'de hino e amen jebbilii…ói, hino e amen kadi oo√Īii…ói. Kala jebbilii ngii, …óin …óoon faandike peewal."
  72,15,"Oo√Īii…ói …óiin kan, …ói laatanike Jahannama oon carmalle."
  72,16,"E won'de si …ďe √Īii…ďuno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Min njarnayno …ďe ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam,"
  72,17,"fii yo Min ndaarndoro …ďe heen. Kala …óuurnii…óo e JaŇčtoore Joomi mum nden, O naaday mo e lepte ca…ótu…óe."
  72,18,"E won'de juulir…óe …óeen ko Allah leeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto."
  72,19,"E won'de tuma jiyaa…óo Allah on darinoo himo rewa mo, …ói …óe…ďuno wa…ó…óondirgol e hoore makko."
  72,20,"Maaku : "nganndee ko Joomi am (tan) mi ndewata, mi kafidataa mo kadi hay e gooto"."
  72,21,"Maaku : "Miin mi waawanaa on du√Īude lorra, wonaa fii poo…óugol nafa"."
  72,22,"Maaku : "Hay gooto waawaa da…óndugol kam e Allah; mi he…ďataa ko woori mo ∆īoo√Īorde"
  72,23,"si wonaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule makko …óeen. Kala jeddu…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, …ďe luttay e magge poomaa."
  72,24,"Haa si …ďe nji'ii ko …ďe kammbirananoo kon, …ďe aray anndude ko hombo …ďuri lo'ode ballo, …ďuri kadi fam…óude limoore."
  72,25,"Maaku : "Mi anndaa si ko kammbirana…óon kon hino …ďadii, maa si koomi am wa…óanat …óuum dumunna."
  72,26,"Ko o ganndo wirnii…ói. O ∆īellintinantaa wirnii…ói makko …óiin hay e gooto."
  72,27,"si wonaa mo o welanaa e Nulaa…óo, o naadnay ye'eso on e …ďaawo makko tommbotoo…ďe."
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu won'de …ďen njottinii nule joomi ma…ď…ďe …óeen. O hu…ďindorii (anndugol) ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon, O mofti limoore kala hu'unde"."